word":"either","count":1},{"word":"ask","count":1},{"word":"outside","count":1},{"word":"fantastic","count":1},{"word":"news","count":1},{"word":"expect","count":1},{"word":"involved","count":1},{"word":"transportation","count":1},{"word":"researchers","count":1},{"word":"able","count":1},{"word":"navigate","count":1},{"word":"ease","count":1},{"word":"huge","count":1},{"word":"resonator","count":1},{"word":"raise","count":1},{"word":"point","count":1},{"word":"break","count":1},{"word":"shield","count":1},{"word":"take","count":1},{"word":"stand","count":1},{"word":"chance","count":1},{"word":"closing","count":1},{"word":"ah","count":1},{"word":"mortefi","count":1},{"word":"finally","count":1},{"word":"deign","count":1},{"word":"respond","count":1},{"word":"calls","count":1},{"word":"eh","count":1},{"word":"curious","count":1},{"word":"happened","count":1},{"word":"arrange","count":1},{"word":"someone","count":1},{"word":"clear","count":1},{"word":"secure","count":1},{"word":"path","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"retrieve","count":1},{"word":"spare","count":1},{"word":"parts","count":1},{"word":"couriers","count":1},{"word":"mimika","count":1},{"word":"courier","count":1},{"word":"looking","count":1},{"word":"waiting","count":1},{"word":"resonance","count":1},{"word":"nexus","count":1},{"word":"adrenaline","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"real","count":1},{"word":"ink","count":1},{"word":"paper","count":1},{"word":"days","count":1},{"word":"hahahaha","count":1},{"word":"powerful","count":1},{"word":"imagined","count":1},{"word":"one-on-one","count":1},{"word":"showdown","count":1},{"word":"criminal","count":1},{"word":"deserted","count":1},{"word":"land","count":1},{"word":"death","count":1},{"word":"claim","count":1},{"word":"bounty","count":1},{"word":"leave","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"cheer","count":1},{"word":"romance","count":1},{"word":"wild","count":1},{"word":"west","count":1},{"word":"message","count":1},{"word":"emergencies","count":1},{"word":"lab","count":1},{"word":"interested","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"donglu","count":1},{"word":"research","count":1},{"word":"station","count":1},{"word":"till","count":1},{"word":"meet","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"A {Male=young man;Female=young lady} transforming into a flaming rider, rushing to the destination with unyielding conviction to charge at the Tacet Mark! Aah... What a beautiful story.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Our observations show that the Tacet Mark core is nearly completely deactivated, so the toxin from the Incinero Petal pollen has almost disappeared.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"The dangerous Gravity Storms that were gathering over the Tacet Mark core have vanished. We can confidently conclude that... Jinzhou is safe now.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Hey, aren't you that Rover? You awake?","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"This is the weather observatory in the Port City of Guixu. You passed out during a battle with the Inferno Rider. Some guys from Lollo Logistics brought you here.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Oh, that's the Tacet Discord you just met. It looks like a rider on a motorbike, so I named it the Inferno Rider. A good name, isn't it?","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Hahaha! That’s right. There’s a reason why we must put it down.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Our detection shows that the anomalous gravity field here is giving birth to a giant storm, which will sweep the pollen of Incinero Petal to the upper air.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"So you know about it. That'll save me the explanation.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Incinero Petal is not a kind of plant, but an animal Tacet Discord. The flower-like structure is actually the end of its limbs.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"To eliminate the Incinero Petals themselves is pointless. To stop the pollen from spreading, we must destroy the Tacet Mark at its core.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Initially, we were thinking about blowing that thing up...","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Technically, it didn't \"come\" to us; it was \"discovered\". That Inferno Rider seems to have been in the depths of Sea of Flames since that crisis many years ago.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Launching a direct assault on the Tacet Mark core deep within the Sea of Flames was already a daunting task, and with this Tacet Discord in play, our mission now seems nearly impossible.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"The special properties of the Sea of Flames make it safer for solo missions, so I've posted the wanted posters, hoping to recruit some skilled Resonators to defeat that TD.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"We don't know either. You should ask the guys from Lollo Logistics who brought you back. They're right outside the observatory.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"You've brought some fantastic news. Didn't expect Lollo Logistics to get involved.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"With their transportation, our researchers should be able to navigate through the Incinero Petals with ease. This is a huge help.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Well, if not even a Resonator like you, {PlayerName}, could defeat it...","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"You raise a good point. We still don’t have a way to break that shield.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"If we can't take the Inferno Rider out, we won't stand a chance closing in on the Tacet Mark core.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Ah, Mortefi. You finally deign to respond to my calls, eh?","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"I'm curious—how do you know so much about what happened back then, being so young?","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"We'll arrange for someone to clear a secure path. {PlayerName}, please help us retrieve the spare parts with the Lollo Logistics couriers.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"By the way, Mimika, the courier, was looking for you. She's waiting at the Resonance Nexus.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Yes. Doesn't it get your adrenaline rushing to see an old poster like this, made with real ink and paper like in the old days? Hahahaha!","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"A powerful one like yourself must have imagined this...","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"...A one-on-one showdown with a wanted criminal on a deserted land of death. Then you claim the bounty and leave as people cheer for you. That is the romance of the wild west!","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Sorry, I've got a message...","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Yes, it’s me... All right, I see.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Sorry, got some emergencies back in my lab... If you're interested in this poster, find me at Donglu Research Station in Port City of Guixu.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"All right. {Male=Young man!;Female=Young lady!} Till we meet next time!","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005}]}